So we won't have a hangout that week.

00:00:54.439 --> 00:00:58.599
But I'm excited to get to meet so many of you there in person.

00:00:58.599 --> 00:01:03.279
But anyways, if you're watching this recording at some point in the future on YouTube, and

00:01:03.279 --> 00:01:09.160
you are thinking, I want to join them live, you can use the link below and the details

00:01:09.160 --> 00:01:11.160
to add it to your calendar too.

00:01:11.160 --> 00:01:16.879
But at the Hangout, we're all dedicated to making this a welcoming environment for everybody.

00:01:16.879 --> 00:01:23.839
We love to hear from everyone, no matter your years of experience, titles, industry or languages

00:01:23.839 --> 00:01:25.959
that you work in too.

