00:16:28.099 --> 00:16:33.739
through these different groups, so different departments, I'm sure, have different things

00:16:33.739 --> 00:16:36.900
that they consider are protected or secure.

00:16:36.900 --> 00:16:43.340
So how did you kind of deal with that challenge of trying to be like, these are the kind of

00:16:43.340 --> 00:16:49.260
tools we've built to ensure security of data within different departments and to assure

00:16:49.260 --> 00:16:54.179
that this is not just all going to be shared across every team or every group?

00:16:54.179 --> 00:16:57.020
